OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,FMurray Goulder, who receives personal
OL,7,Findependence payments because of his
OL,8,Fepilepsy, told ITV News he believes
OL,9,Fwelfare cuts are an "attack" on
OL,10,Fdisabled people.
OL,12,FAn epilepsy sufferer who relies on
OL,13,Fbenefits to get to work has claimed
OL,14,Fthe government's decision to reform
OL,15,Fthe system is an "attack" on disabled
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,FMurray Goulder works full-time at
OL,19,FRoyal Mail and receives personal
OL,20,Findependence payments (Pip) because of
OL,21,Fhis epilepsy.
