OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,FWhile he believes the current system
OL,7,Fis "broken" and needs reform, he
OL,8,Fworries about the impact budget cuts
OL,9,Fmay have on those with disabilities.
OL,11,FHe said: "They (the government) may
OL,12,Fneed money for defence and stuff like
OL,13,Fthat, but I don't see how they've come
OL,14,Fto the conclusion that you should then
OL,15,Fgo and attack disabled people."
