OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,FThe government wants to get more
OL,7,Fpeople into work through changes to
OL,8,Fthe benefits system, but Murray says
OL,9,F"not everyone in that group doesn't
OL,10,Fwant to work" and the "rhetoric puts
OL,11,Feveryone under the same cloud."
OL,13,FHe added: "There'll be a proportion
OL,14,Fthat can't work and there's no way
OL,15,Fthat they can. And that includes
OL,16,Fpeople with my condition."
