OL,6,F"It's been a long time that I've had
OL,7,Fthe condition, I've tried lots of
OL,8,Fmedications, but it can be
OL,9,Ffrightening."
OL,11,FAs a result, Murray says he needs
OL,12,Fsupport getting to and from work and
OL,13,Foften has to get taxis because he
OL,14,Fcan't use public transport when he's
OL,15,Fon his own.
