OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,FThe government unveiled its
OL,7,Fcontroversial welfare reforms on
OL,8,FTuesday, promising to create a "pro-
OL,9,Fwork" culture and fix a "broken
OL,10,Fsystem," as ITV News Horry Horton and
OL,11,FAnushka Asthana report
OL,13,FIn addition, his condition means he
OL,14,Fgets a lot of headaches, and while he
OL,15,Freceives prescription medication,
OL,16,Fthere are some which aren't prescribed
OL,17,Fand that can be costly.
