OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,FMurray's personal independence
OL,7,Fpayments help cover some of those
OL,8,Fextra costs - which add up to around
OL,9,F#750 a month.
OL,11,FUnder the government's plans,
OL,12,Feligibility criteria for Pip will be
OL,13,Ftightened, with people having to prove
OL,14,Fmore severe difficulties to qualify.
OL,16,FCurrently people applying are given
OL,17,Fpoints based on how much they need
OL,18,Fsupport with everyday activities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
