OL,3,CEpilepsy sufferer says welfare cuts an
OL,4,C'attack' on disabled people
OL,6,F"I've always said that the simple and
OL,7,Feasy way of doing this is not to have
OL,8,Fone system to judge everyone, not have
OL,9,Fone piece of paperwork that everyone
OL,10,Fjust fills in generically.
OL,12,F"So if you're going to give it for
OL,13,Fmental health, have a mental health
OL,14,Fone. If you're going to give it for
OL,15,Fneurological conditions, a
OL,16,Fneurological pathway, and the other
OL,17,Fone should be for people with physical
OL,18,Fdisabilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
