OL,6,F"It should just never have been put in
OL,7,Fplace in the first place if this is
OL,8,Fwhat they were going to do," Murray
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FHe continued: "I feel personally that
OL,12,Fthe government is weaponising disabled
OL,13,Fpeople to help pay for defence."
